'''''Mosonngoa''''' ni  filimi  yo muri  Mosotho yasohotse  2014 ikaba filime ngufi iyobowe na Lemohang Yeremiya Mosese kandi yakozwe na Hannah Stockmann. <ref>https://mubi.com/films/mosonngoa</ref> Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Siphiwe Nzima-Ntskhe mu mwanya wa mbere mu gihe Masele Tokane, Chaka Phehlamarole Khalechene na Retselisitsoe Sekake bagize uruhare runini. <ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/co/film848919.html</ref><ref>http://rwanda.spla.pro/file.film.mosonngoa-the-mocked-one.17406.html</ref>

Filime yakiriwe neza nabayinenga kandi yerekanwa mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/work/2036508/</ref> <ref>http://www.luxorafricanfilmfestival.com/en/PastEditions/2015/Film/Short%20Films/Mosonngoa%20The%20Mocked%20One</ref>

